but specialists complain privately that just as in the 1987 crash , the `` unk '' firms -- big investment banks that support the market by trading big blocks of stock -- stayed on the sidelines during friday 's unk . mr. phelan said , `` it will take another day or two '' to analyze who was buying and selling friday .
