with considerable irony , the case also shows how completely japan has turned the tables on u.s. business . americans used to complain bitterly about being unk by unk products from japan . now sony , whose innovative , unk products are among the most unk in consumer electronics , is bitterly complaining about a little u.s. firm with a cheap unk produced in china .
