in addition , sen. unk last week disclosed that he unk had paid $ unk to american continental as unk for trips he and his family took aboard the corporate jet to mr. keating 's vacation home at cat unk , the unk , from 1984 through 1986 . sen. unk said he had meant to pay for the trips at the time but that the matter `` fell between the cracks . ''
