still , such a pricing strategy just might appeal to people like unk bates , a unk in the journal survey . she recently walked out of a furniture store because the salesman offered to cut the price of a unk unk three times . when a store keeps dropping prices , the unk , mich. , resident says , `` i get unk that they 're trying to get the most they can out of you . ''
